@node "107" "107"
@prev "106bf"

 SystemX (eSSeXX) v1.07

 SX        - if a Door wont found there may come a possible
             Endlessloop - Fixed

           - reworked the Testdoor procedure

           - new XIM-Command 1516 SX_MSGAREANUM
             to retrive the current MsgArea number
 
           - internal SysopPage:
             ...complete rewrote the Chat-routine
             ...added a wordwrapping for chat
             ...MCP displays correct activity after chat
 
           - change the source architecture a bit
  
           - wildcard '*' support on login-handle allowed now
             String added in sx:TXT/Strings.ANS

           - 'About' text and welcome message bumped
  
 SX-Config - SystemX can handle up to 32 nodes again

 SX-MCP    - bumped version


 @{"MAIN" link "MAIN" 0}
@endnode

